reviews.text:
Tried the rich extract latte.
It tastes a bit weird, not sure is it because it‚Äôs heavily extracted.
Taste very bitter. Especially after the ice melt, it tastes very diluted.

Staff very friendly.
Would say the coffee is decent and also had their refreshing Zesty Pamelo which is very sweet and tangy. If only I can request for less sweet. Anyway I enjoyed my drinks ! The staff are friendly too.
